C

CardType - Enum in it.polimi.ingsw.ps21
Used to enumerate the different types of the cards The game contains 6 different types of cards: Territory Cards (Green cards) Building Cards (Yellow cards) Character Cards (Blue cards) Venture Cards (Purple cards) Excommunication cards Leader cards (used in Advanced Matches)
countBlueCards() - Method in class it.polimi.ingsw.ps21.model.Player
Returns the number of the character (blue) cards that the player has acquired during the game.
countCards(CardType) - Method in class it.polimi.ingsw.ps21.model.Player
Returns the number of the cards of a specified type owned by the player.
countGreenCards() - Method in class it.polimi.ingsw.ps21.model.Player
Returns the number of the territory (green) cards that the player has acquired during the game.
countPurpleCards() - Method in class it.polimi.ingsw.ps21.model.Player
Returns the number of the venture (purple) cards that the player has acquired during the game.
countYellowCards() - Method in class it.polimi.ingsw.ps21.model.Player
Returns the number of the building (yellow) cards that the player has acquired during the game.
CurrentModifier - Class in it.polimi.ingsw.ps21.model
This class is used to store modifiers that may have effects on each action of the player.
